context.text: List of communes of Luxembourg in different languages - Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia

The English name is often the same as the French version, on account of the primacy of the French language in official and legislative matters in Luxembourg and the historical relationship and rivalry between France and the United Kingdom .
List of communes of Luxembourg in different languages

This is a list of the communes of Luxembourg in different languages . Luxembourg has three official tongues ( Luxembourgish , French , and German ), so each commune can have up to three different official names.
